title.narrative: Sahel 2013 monitoring, evaluation and consultancy costs

description.narrative: This activity (Sahel 2013 monitoring, evaluation and consultancy costs) is a component of UK humanitarian response in the Sahel 2013 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £635,242. This component benefits South of Sahara, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Food assistance. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 27-06-2013 and the end date is 30-11-2014.
